<HEADLINE>  COUPLE IN DINGO CASE WINS $320,000  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>     The baby, Azaria, vanished from the couple's campsite near Ayers Rock in
central Australia in August 1980. Her body was never found.;    In 1982, Lindy
Chamberlain was convicted of murder. Her husband was found guilty of being an
accessory after the fact.;    Many people said they believed Lindy Chamberlain
